===吳語短暫復興===
吳語電視全盛時期，在學生流傳甚廣。<ref name="李军林2011"/>學術研究普遍指出在家看電視對於[[語言習得|語言習得]]的潛移默化，比學校的語言教學更有效。<ref name="Kuppens2010b">{{cite journal|title=Incidental foreign language acquisition from media exposure|journal=Learning, Media and Technology |date=2010|volume=35|issue=1|last=Kuppens|first=An H. |url=|archiveurl=|archivedate=|page=66-67, 79-80|quote=Thus, media technologies are not only useful for intentional language learning but also for incidental language acquisition. (...) In addition to these studies on the incidental acquisition of a ''foreign'' language through television, there is research that confirms the incidental acquisition of a ''second language'' (i.e., by bilinguals; see, e.g., Uchikoshi 2005, 2006a, 2006b) and of a ''native'' language (e.g., Krcmar, Grela, and Lin 2007;Rice et al. 1990; Wright et al. 2001) from television viewing. (...) Incidental and intentional language acquisition are very different processes when it comes to, for instance, the object of focus of the learner's attention (meaning vs. form), the amount of exposure needed (more vs. less; see, e.g., Gass 1999, 322), and the degree of (teacher) supervision and feedback (none vs. some). }}</ref>在家裡也跟父母只講普通話的本地兒童（又參見[[無方言族|無方言族]]），因看電視而重拾一些吳語單詞，例如寧波的[[汉语译制片|吳語譯製片]]節目《[[阿國電影|阿國電影]]》和紹興的《[[师爷说新闻|师爷说新闻]]》甚受學習者喜愛。<ref>{{citenews|title=小宁波人只说普通话不说宁波话(图)|newspaper=搜狐新聞——轉自[[现代金报|现代金报]]|date=2007-03-11|last=宗珵|last2=周科娜|url=https://news.sohu.com/20070311/n248646351.shtml|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070313225037/https://news.sohu.com/20070311/n248646351.shtml|archivedate=2007-03-13|accessdate=2021-01-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="罗昕2012"/>

